《'''泥土'''》（{{lang-en|'''''Mud'''''}}）是一部2012年由[[杰夫·尼科尔斯|杰夫·尼科尔斯]]编剧并执导的美国剧情片。主演是[[馬修·麥康納希|馬修·麥康納希]]、[[泰·謝里丹|泰·謝里丹]]、[[雅各布·洛夫蘭|雅各布·洛夫蘭]]、[[山姆·夏普德|山姆·夏普德]]和[[麗絲·韋花絲潘|麗絲·韋花絲潘]]。入围[[第65届戛纳电影节|第65届戛纳电影节]]主竞赛单元<ref name="Official Selection">{{cite web |url=http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/58878.html |title=2012 Official Selection |accessdate=19 April 2012 |work=Cannes |archive-date=2017-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322102818/http://www.festival-cannes.fr/en/article/58878.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="timeout">{{cite web |url=http://www.timeout.com/london/feature/2547/cannes-film-festival-2012-line-up-announced |title=Cannes Film Festival 2012 line-up announced |accessdate=19 April 2012 |work=Timeout |archive-date=2013-03-18 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6FCWRe4qC?url=http://www.timeout.com/london/film/cannes-film-festival-2012-line-up-announced |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于2013年1月在[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]上亮相，同年4月26日在美国[[有限上映|有限上映]]。<ref>{{cite news| title = Mud Trailer: Matthew McConaughey and Reese Witherspoon Have a Southern-Accent-Off| work = Vulture| date = 2013-01-16| url = http://www.vulture.com/2013/01/watch-matthew-mcconaughey-in-the-mud-trailer.html| accessdate = 2013-01-16| first = Jesse David| last = Fox| archive-date = 2019-07-15| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190715105336/https://www.vulture.com/2013/01/watch-matthew-mcconaughey-in-the-mud-trailer.html| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| title ='Mud' trailer with Matthew McConaughey reignites the fuse in advance of Sundance bow| work =Hitflix| date =2013-01-16| url =http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/mud-trailer-with-matthew-mcconaughey-reignites-the-fuse-in-advance-of-sundance-bow| accessdate =2013-01-16| first =Kristopher| last =Tapley| archive-date =2016-03-04| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304215415/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/mud-trailer-with-matthew-mcconaughey-reignites-the-fuse-in-advance-of-sundance-bow| dead-url =no}}</r